CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

April 1, 2005

[Cite as 04/01/2005 Case Announcements, 2005-Ohio-1502.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2005-0023. Duke Realty Ohio v. Hamilton Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 2003-T-1751. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals. On January 20, 2005, this case was referred to mediation under S.Ct.Prac.R. XIV(6).

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that the parties show cause within fourteen days of the date of this entry why this court should not return this case to the regular docket.
